OL,3,CStreeting to 'look at' mental capacity
OL,4,Claw change after murder of autistic man
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,7,Fconfirmed he will "look at" a proposed
OL,8,Flaw change to the way mental capacity
OL,9,Fassessments are carried out, after ITV
OL,10,FNews revealed concerns that some
OL,11,Fvulnerable adults are not receiving
OL,12,Fvital support.
OL,14,FThree cross-party MPs, including one
OL,15,Fof Streeting's predecessors Jeremy
OL,16,FHunt, are urging the government to
OL,17,Fmake a key change to the new Mental
OL,18,FHealth Bill that would ensure the
OL,19,Fviews of family members are taken into
OL,20,Faccount when deciding whether an adult
OL,21,Fneeds a mental capacity assessment.
