OL,3,CStreeting to 'look at' mental capacity
OL,4,Claw change after murder of autistic man
OL,6,FITV News spoke to the mother of 24-
OL,7,Fyear-old Christopher Laskaris, a
OL,8,Fvulnerable, autistic man who was
OL,9,Fmurdered in his own home by a
OL,10,Fconvicted criminal who took over his
OL,11,Fflat and exploited him. Despite years
OL,12,Fof his mother Fiona pleading for help
OL,13,Ffor her son, he was never given a
OL,14,Fmental capacity assessment to
OL,15,Fdetermine what support he needed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
