OL,3,CStreeting to 'look at' mental capacity
OL,4,Claw change after murder of autistic man
OL,6,FFiona, backed by the MPs and the
OL,7,FNational Autistic Society, now wants
OL,8,Fthe law changed to make sure other
OL,9,Fvulnerable adults and their families
OL,10,Fdon't have to suffer the way her
OL,11,Ffamily have.
OL,13,FThe health secretary said: "The issue
OL,14,Fthey're raising - I absolutely agree
OL,15,Fwith them - is an issue.
OL,17,F"I haven't actually seen their
OL,18,Famendment yet but I'm certainly open
OL,19,Fto looking at their case because I
OL,20,Frecognise the issue they're trying to
OL,21,Fraise."
