OL,3,CStreeting to 'look at' mental capacity
OL,4,Claw change after murder of autistic man
OL,6,F"One of the problems in Christopher's
OL,7,Fcase was that when mental capacity
OL,8,Fassessments should have been carried
OL,9,Fout, they weren't, because they were
OL,10,Fjust assuming that he had capacity,"
OL,11,Fhis mother Fiona previously told ITV
OL,12,FNews.
OL,14,F"They were taking his responses at
OL,15,Fface value and they weren't checking
OL,16,Fthat he fully understood the decisions
OL,17,Fhe was making and the likely
OL,18,Fconsequences of making them...
