OL,3,CStreeting to 'look at' mental capacity
OL,4,Claw change after murder of autistic man
OL,6,F"And Christopher wanted to please
OL,7,Fpeople around him. So, if people were
OL,8,Fsaying to him 'you don't need support,
OL,9,Fdo you?', he'd just say, 'yes, I'm
OL,10,Ffine'."
OL,12,FShe added: "I just tried everything I
OL,13,Fcould for years and years, trying to
OL,14,Fget him the help and support he
OL,15,Fneeded, trying to get him down here
OL,16,F(to Surrey)... I was constantly having
OL,17,Fto ring up the police just to check he
OL,18,Fwas okay. For any mother to be left in
OL,19,Fthat position with a vulnerable child
OL,20,F- the anguish, it's the sort of worst
OL,21,Ftorture you can inflict on a mother.
