OL,3,CStreeting to 'look at' mental capacity
OL,4,Claw change after murder of autistic man
OL,6,F"And that's why I want the law
OL,7,Fchanged. I want parents listened to so
OL,8,Fthat no one else has to go through
OL,9,Fthis - years and years of trying to
OL,10,Fget help for your disabled child."
OL,12,FThe MPs' concerns around the law being
OL,13,Fmisapplied and misappropriated are
OL,14,Fshared among many within the medical
OL,15,Fand charity sectors. The issues have
OL,16,Fbeen raised in research conducted by
OL,17,Fthe BMJ, the Independent Review of the
OL,18,FMental Health Act and as far back as
OL,19,Fthe 2014 House of Lords Select
OL,20,FCommittee's post-legislative scrutiny
OL,21,Fof the Mental Capacity Act.
